v/n2007042321 http://lccn.loc.gov/sh85000624 http://lccn.loc.gov/sh2008111662 http://lccn.loc.gov/sh85036372" n="1" xml:id="Uk_Lahore_136-137-item1"><textLang mainLang="fa">Persian </textLang><note><p><title key="work_22378">Kharīd'nāmah</title> or deed of purchase in the form of an <title key="work_22378">iqrār'nāmah-'i sharʿī</title> or agreement under Islamic law, confirming that <persName key="person_f8290" role="subject">Rāmdayāl ibn Sadānand ibn Santūkh (Santokh) Rāy Khatrī</persName> purchased in its entirety the maqarr or residence (description), located within the ḥiṣār or fort of <placeName>dār al-salṭanah Lāhawr</placeName> (details), through <persName key="person_f8291" role="subject">Dattāmal ibn Sūhan (Sohan) Laʿl ibn Rājā Rām Khatrī Mihrūtrah (Mehrotra)</persName>, for the sum of two hundred and thirteen rūpyah and twelve ānah. Custody was taken from ʿ<persName key="person_f8292" role="subject">Abd al-Salīm Mistrī</persName>, with not a dām or darb left outstanding. 
                        </p><p>Dated 16 Sāvan 1901, equating to 11 Rajab 1260/27 July 1844. 
</p><p>Seal impression affixed above text. 
</p><p>Invocation above seal. 
</p><p>Rough shikastah āmīz. Seal in nastaʿlīq. 
</p><p>Scroll, damaged; cropped along text edge, torn, creased, stains, discoloured tape marks. </p><p>Brown paper on cloth backing. 
